Nazarenko, V. Yu. The new record of Notaris maerkeli (Coleoptera: Curculionidae: Brachycerinae) from Ukraine. Summary. Stenommatomorphus hexarthrus gen. et sp. nov. (Dryophthoridae: Stromboscerinae) is described from the Late Eocene Rovno amber. This is the first fossil representative of the subfamily.
